            "notes": "The key theme of this deck revolves around utilizing the aggressive playstyle of Spider-Man 2099 to control the game through a mix of burn spells, counterspells, and disruptive spells. The deck aims to maintain tempo by deploying threats like Malcolm, Alluring Scoundrel and True-Name Nemesis while disrupting the opponent's game plan with spells like Spell Pierce, Force of Negation, and Remand. The deck's mana base is carefully constructed to support its two-color identity, with a blend of fetch lands, shock lands, and utility lands like Mystic Sanctuary and Swarmyard. By combining efficient creatures and versatile spells, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent and secure victory through strategic gameplay."
